“As iron sharpens iron, so one man sharpens another.”
‭‭Proverbs‬ ‭27‬:‭17‬ ‭

Excited for my brothers @ant_thechamp_cassar & @moose_777 to step into the @ikonfightingchampionship cage tomorrow night. Tune in on @ufcfightpass at 8pm

My brothers. We win together, we lose together. That’s what family does. I couldn’t be more proud of @ant_thechamp_cassar & @moose_777 

I’m grateful to be on this journey with likeminded men who prioritize family and character over money and ego. Our success is inevitable and our foundation is uncompromising. It’s our time.

Going into my training sessions I’m always nervous. I know I push myself to the absolute limit and frankly it’s terrifying. Leading up to it there’s part of me that says, “just take this one easy” or “you don’t need to go so hard”. This is when I ask myself, “do you want to be champ or not? Do you want this life or not?” We always have a choice. I choose to kill myself in training, and feel all of that pain, that way I can be confident and compete like an absolute intelligent savage. So my body is ready to cash the checks my will and skill are writing (@treigning_lab quote). This is the life I choose, I live it everyday.
